definitions.definition: A province of Soccsksargen , Mindanao , Philippines . Capital and largest city: Kidapawan .
A former province of Mindanao , Philippines ; modern Cotabato , Maguindanao , South Cotabato , or Sultan Kudarat . Capital and largest city: Cotabato City .
